item.description:

You’re missing brackets… undo everything you did or backup your client.java.

item.title: Compile server error
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

It’s not a ‘barket’. It’s called a brace.
These are braces - ().
In your case, you have too many closing braces before your multiCombat method. Delete a few.
